          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I was just today years old when I learned there’s valet parking for Bass Pro Shop at the Pyramid in Memphis, Tennessee. Every time I’ve been to one or a Cabela’s I’ve had to park my own vehicle, but after learning about a theft scheme involving the valet-parked cars that might be the preferable way.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
